I was able to visit the ambassador on that day, and we spoke about my experience in Mauritania. Ravi about that kind of culture. I had to explain my time in both Aurelle and No-(could be the reason you were not there). Even though I didn’t eat bolao, (the traditional healthy food that you are from) I still tasted a lot of cow…I mean human flesh on the street.

Dear Highlights,

I am a nice person. I know that there are a lot of people that say things about my attitude on the

Internet, but most of the time I’m lying to get your attention. I want to be sincere for a change. You were right about La Lunette – I do not like you very much. I like Maurice N’those other guys from China, but you are just not my cup of tea. Similar to those Pudra students that were complaining.
